{"tid":721600,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［畫電話殼］深夜作畫","createTime":"2018-06-28T19:38:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T22:59:33.000Z","uid":62754,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1ca1ed9353932b574ed7c70bf76be2119118d7b9","tid":721600,"uid":62754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T19:38:48.000Z","msg":"半夜好悶搵野做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗起之前買左幾個透明phone case<br />\n又好耐冇揸起枝畫筆<br />\n就畫phone case啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：畫畫唔叻 多多指教<br />\n<br />\n首先準備：<br />\nAcrylic（你中意嘅顏色）<br />\n唔要嘅淨色/透明phone case<br />\n畫具（畫筆、毛巾、洗筆器etc.）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/033252_d2c89d20efe5d5039511f7009cbcb698.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F033252_d2c89d20efe5d5039511f7009cbcb698.png&h=5442669b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我就用呢啲色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後求其將啲Acrylic噠上去<br />\n咩色都噠啲<br />\n趁未乾嘅時候就好噠其他色上去<br />\n等顏色同顏色之間唔好太唔融合<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/033739_9fd498da9eb467d44be783b6d6fa68db.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F033739_9fd498da9eb467d44be783b6d6fa68db.png&h=2258fe29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁就完成第一層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b51c9fdb8342ba0a8f522d27d95b43c41dc9c5a5","tid":721600,"uid":62754,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T19:47:55.000Z","msg":"係咪冇人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcbce544bc3c5815c2ef186dd076d36f4b2224ab","tid":721600,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T19:49:00.000Z","msg":"睇緊 繼續"},{"pid":"2b812af2848cde093eb113aa99be4bb22fcb4908","tid":721600,"uid":52282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T19:49:43.000Z","msg":"睇緊 繼續"},{"pid":"1a62c77b462bb2e0f13cd0eddbf334be63ce4dc5","tid":721600,"uid":45250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T19:50:07.000Z","msg":"Do it"},{"pid":"ca90f71578406a500ccc9eea89f75abc112bd624","tid":721600,"uid":62754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T19:58:28.000Z","msg":"第二層上浸淺色啲嘅<br />\n主要係中間大範圍上淺色<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/035729_8ff4bcd5a04c761edb3494598a92eca0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F035729_8ff4bcd5a04c761edb3494598a92eca0.png&h=d4ea77da&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/035731_776654fd84247ed279fa09b284a20009.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F035731_776654fd84247ed279fa09b284a20009.png&h=72469fcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一張有閃光燈 一張冇"},{"pid":"48eb80cebe071d2a7592e20030bcdcc569dc7c4f","tid":721600,"uid":126466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T19:59:45.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"0d535dcf3b69b00dc8edec6d7a9f30ce5c5f57f3","tid":721600,"uid":87257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T20:00:51.000Z","msg":"睇緊 繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dba6ccf9628b1a694813fdc3b20235404eb904f7","tid":721600,"uid":29649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T20:03:10.000Z","msg":"睇緊 繼續"},{"pid":"001d0d7f91583d26eaf38143096ee853bcae98ae","tid":721600,"uid":62754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T20:03:48.000Z","msg":"畫緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec28c29add919a0b6102ec9da34520172aecaff0","tid":721600,"uid":7359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T20:03:48.000Z","msg":"咁夜唔訓？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bec88ad2e938a1e211c93262babfcea7bbfdac67","tid":721600,"uid":151187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec28c29add919a0b6102ec9da34520172aecaff0","tid":721600,"uid":7359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T20:03:48.000Z","msg":"咁夜唔訓？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T20:04:13.000Z","msg":"你都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22a06a76414f755fe8db6ffbdc83c1cfa41840de","tid":721600,"uid":62754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec28c29add919a0b6102ec9da34520172aecaff0","tid":721600,"uid":7359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T20:03:48.000Z","msg":"咁夜唔訓？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T20:04:16.000Z","msg":"生理時鐘錯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef82e66a683995440b78909b2a5ef56dd32fa0dc","tid":721600,"uid":84297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T20:04:27.000Z","msg":"睇緊 繼續"},{"pid":"6b7adacbac73b8a2e575dbb7e20f8c621c22bebb","tid":721600,"uid":62754,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T20:16:45.000Z","msg":"其實都畫得八八九九<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我加咗少少波波上去<img src